`-Xms1g -Xmx2g -XX:+PrintGCDetails -Xlog:gc+cpu=info -Xlog:gc+heap+exit`&lt;br&gt;
**you will get ~5-6 GC runs (tested with java 11+16 hotspot vm) .**&lt;br&gt;GC Epsilon tests clearly shows that it can run without any GCing.

**Challenge:**&lt;br&gt;Can you find jvm arguments which will force G1 to not do any GCing here?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

